idate. We find that the CPDs are detectable in all 3 signposts with ALMA\nCycle 3 capabilities for both 1 and 5 M_Jup protoplanets, when embedded in an\nisothermal disk.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 May 2015 05:15:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 Nov 2015 18:01:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-04"}
