ator border regime, and (iii)\nKondo-lattice limit when the $f$-electron occupancy is very close to the $f$\nelectrons half-filling, $\\langle\\hat n_{f}\\rangle\\rightarrow1$. The non-Landau\nfeatures of emerging correlated quantum liquid state are stressed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 May 2015 15:22:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Aug 2015 07:23:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-22"}
